SUMMARY:Nosh With Your Neighbors
DESCRIPTION:Join fellow Older Adults for a bring-your-own Kosher style lunch. This is a great place to meet your neighbors\, connect with your Jewish community\, and enjoy a meal in the company of friends new and old! Experience a taste of arts and culture with your meal. Desserts\, coffee\, and tea are provided.  \nNosh meets monthly on the second Thursday of the month. \n_____________________________________________ \nFor more information email Gravity: gravity.goldberg@jcceastbay.org 
URL:https://jcceastbay.org/events/nosh-with-your-neighbors-1-2026/2026-05-14/
LOCATION:JCC East Bay\, 1414 Walnut Street\, Berkeley\, CA\, 94709\, United States
CATEGORIES:Older Adults
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://jcceastbay.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Nosh-With-Your-Neighbors-web-event.png
END:VEVENT
